            What is Github
        ========================


Github is a code hosting platform for Collaboration and version control

Github lets you (and others) work together on projects




Repository
=================


A github Repository can be used to store a development projects

it can contain folders and any type of files(html , css, javacscript)



Why version control is needed 
========================================


in real life projects generally have multipler developers
working in parallel so in a version control system like 
git is needed to ensure there are no code conflict
between the developers




Git merge conflict
=========================

A merge conflict is an event that takes place when 
git is unable to automatically resolve difference in code 
between two commits are on different branches


